FeedPackage.Description: Task hierarchy and resource scheduling components for Silverlight™ 4 / WPF and .NET 4: Gantt Chart, Schedule Chart, Load Chart; PERT Chart, Network Diagram. Main features: Interactive task hierarchy management, resource scheduling, resource load, and project flow charts; Task bars and dependency lines with drag and drop support; Copy and paste operations, undo queue; Working time, scales, and zoom level customization; Project baseline visualization, critical path enumeration; Resource leveling algorithm; Support to display multiple assignment lines in a single row; Data binding with high customizability; Increased performance for large sets of data; Rich user experience, customizable appearance, culture awareness; Customizable printing and image exporting; Two-way Microsoft Project® XML compatibility; Model-View-ViewModel (MVVM) pattern support (Prism).
FeedPackage.ReleaseNotes: New features: drag and drop support for creating all dependency types, updating tool tips, built-in item identifier properties, miscellaneous corrections and multiple performance improvements.
FeedPackage.Summary: Task hierarchy and resource scheduling components for Silverlight™ 4 / WPF and .NET 4: Gantt Chart, Schedule Chart, Load Chart; PERT Chart, Network Diagram.
FeedPackage.Tags: Gantt schedule PERT chart project task management Silverlight WPF LightSwitch
